### Legacy Gaming API Tests (Token-based)

@authToken =
@newUserID =

### 1. SignInfo.php - Gaming API (requires Authorization token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/gaming/api/SignInfo.php
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

_format=json

### 2. SignOut.php - Gaming API (requires Authorization token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/gaming/api/SignOut.php
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

_format=json

### 3. SignUp.php - Gaming API
POST {{baseUrl}}/gaming/api/SignUp.php
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

_format=json&userEmail=gamingtest@test.com&userPassword=PASSWORD_gaming&userName=gaminguser&firstName=Gaming&lastName=User&country=US&city=NewYork

> {%
  client.global.set("newUserID", response.body.values.userID);
%}

### 4. Users.php?f=Update - Gaming API (with userID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/gaming/api/Users.php?f=Update
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

_format=json&userID={{newUserID}}&firstName=UpdatedGaming&lastName=UserUpdated&country=GB&city=London

### 5. Users.php?f=Update - Gaming API (with Authorization token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/gaming/api/Users.php?f=Update
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

_format=json&firstName=GamingTokenUpdated&lastName=UserToken&country=FR&city=Paris&favoriteTeam=PSG

### 6. Teams.php?f=GetCurrentMembers - Get team's current members
POST {{baseUrl}}/gaming/api/Teams.php?f=GetCurrentMembers
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

_format=json&teamID={{testTeamID}}

### 7. Teams.php?f=WaiverMembersDetail - Get waiver members for team
POST {{baseUrl}}/gaming/api/Teams.php?f=WaiverMembersDetail
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

_format=json&teamID={{testTeamID}}

### 8. Teams.php?f=SetRealMembersRanking - Set member ranking (requires token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/gaming/api/Teams.php?f=SetRealMembersRanking
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

_format=json&teamID={{testTeamID}}&memberKeys=P1,T2,P3

### 9. Teams.php?f=WishListSet - Set wish list (requires token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/gaming/api/Teams.php?f=WishListSet
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

_format=json&teamID={{testTeamID}}&wishListKeys=P10.T20

### 10. Teams.php?f=SetFranchiseWishList - Set franchise wish list (requires token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/gaming/api/Teams.php?f=SetFranchiseWishList
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

_format=json&teamID={{testTeamID}}&franchiseWishListKeys=P100,T50
